---
title: Cheesy Pork & Slaw Burger with Homemade Beetroot Relish & Zesty Fries
description: When you’re making a burger, you want all the works. A pork patty on top of garlic aioli (also perfect for dipping the fries in) and
some fresh slaw is all you need to make a delicious burger, but bring it to the next level with a beetroot relish and a bit of zest on
the fries.
